<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Oct 2021 07:44:06 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>小米「米家 K 歌咪高風」   一鍵去人聲 + 雙人連線 + 內置錄音</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/MdWpj0c0BVQ/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[牙 Step]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 06 Oct 2021 07:43:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[小米]]></category><category><![CDATA[米家 K 歌咪高風]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1064157</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>在疫情之下，人們已經很少機會出街「唱 K」。早幾年有所謂的「唱 K 神器」，在播歌同時提供咪高風功能。而近日小 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在疫情之下，人們已經很少機會出街「唱 K」。早幾年有所謂的「唱 K 神器」，在播歌同時提供咪高風功能。而近日小米亦推出了「米家 K 歌咪高風」，並配有消除原唱、雙人無線連線和內置錄音等多項功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1064191 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750655-7b8c48c62edb0eb572e1a8c26fd75c23-694x458.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750655-7b8c48c62edb0eb572e1a8c26fd75c23-694x458.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750655-7b8c48c62edb0eb572e1a8c26fd75c23-768x507.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750655-7b8c48c62edb0eb572e1a8c26fd75c23.jpeg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1064199 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750649-b3d7c452cd623ec70348f9708920d812-694x458.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750649-b3d7c452cd623ec70348f9708920d812-694x458.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750649-b3d7c452cd623ec70348f9708920d812-768x507.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750649-b3d7c452cd623ec70348f9708920d812.jpeg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>米家 K 歌咪高風有消除原唱人聲功能，只需要按下一個按鈕就能夠智能消除原音。另外，產品搭載 16mm 心型指向咪高風和四向發聲揚聲器。並搭載 DSP 晶片，支持 ECHO 混音效果，並利用演算法美化人聲、降噪和抑制嘯叫（咪高風和揚聲器之間產生的高頻聲音）。內置 2500mAh 容量鋰電池，續航力長達 7 小時。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1064192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750643-607387922f780812d25c3415f9997c00-694x458.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750643-607387922f780812d25c3415f9997c00-694x458.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750643-607387922f780812d25c3415f9997c00-768x507.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750643-607387922f780812d25c3415f9997c00.jpeg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>米家 K 歌咪高風亦支持兩支咪之間的無線連接功能，用戶可以透過這個功能進行合唱。而且內置錄音功能，用戶可以錄下自己唱歌的表現。產品提供 9 種趣味音效，包括「領導講話音效」、「卡通音效」和「怪獸音效」等。建議售價為 299 元人民幣（約港幣 360 元）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1064193 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750637-622fdaecd0546280ca2a49aa6eb76088-694x458.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750637-622fdaecd0546280ca2a49aa6eb76088-694x458.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750637-622fdaecd0546280ca2a49aa6eb76088-768x507.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1632750637-622fdaecd0546280ca2a49aa6eb76088.jpeg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p1">資料來源：小米</p>
